each other in a long time.

112
00:05:38,367 --> 00:05:40,967
Di sana, sediakan ruang anda
kalau itu isunya.

113
00:05:41,367 --> 00:05:42,767
Kita tidak perlu bercakap.

114
00:05:42,767 --> 00:05:44,433
[CHESKA MENGERIKAN]

115
00:05:44,433 --> 00:05:45,600
Tunggu sekejap.

116
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:48,767
Awak tak dengar pun
kepada ucapan Seni

117
