118
00:05:50,367 --> 00:05:54,467
Bukankah dia berkata begitu
dengan siapa anda melakukannya?

119
00:05:54,900 --> 00:05:58,700
Dia cakap macam tu
anda boleh melakukan tugas itu.

120
00:05:59,833 --> 00:06:01,833
Awak tak ambil kisah pun
untuk mengaplikasikannya sendiri.

121
00:06:01,833 --> 00:06:04,667
[MOODY MUSIC PLAYING]

122
00:06:04,667 --> 00:06:05,633
[TRIXIE MENGEJUT]

123
00:06:06,067 --> 00:06:07,633
You're giving me a headache.

124
00:06:08,467 --> 00:06:15,433
[KIPAS BERBUANG]

125
00:06:19,433 --> 00:06:20,433
